    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe your eyes when you see this beauty\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and sparkling clean. It's in pristine shape and drives like an absolute dream. If you've been looking for that perfect ride that's been loved and well-maintained, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
