    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated precision, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with its high-pressure dual-VANOS system and six individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual and a variable M-differential lock, ensuring peak torque distribution. Mechanically peerless, the chassis has undergone full subframe reinforcement and a complete bushing refresh to maintain factory kinematic geometry. With zero oxidative wear on the undercarriage and a paint depth consistent with a factory finish, this specimen operates at peak thermal efficiency and structural rigidity. A true collector-grade example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
