    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade vehicle that represents the pinnacle of its model year. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like factory shine and zero imperfections. The interior is equally pristine, featuring supple leather seating with no signs of wear, intact original trim, and a cabin that still retains its new-car scent. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operates with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is showroom-clean; the vehicle has been maintained exclusively by certified specialists with a full service history available. It delivers a tight, responsive driving experience with no mechanical noise or undercarriage oxidation. Complete with all original keys, books, and a clean title, this is a rare find for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
