    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dings, and that interior? Spotless. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, always kept in the garage and pampered with regular detailing. If you're looking for a ride that feels and smells brand new without the dealership headache, this gem is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
