      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring the integrity of the rear suspension geometry under high-torque loads. Mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable locking differential, the mechanical sympathy of this vehicle is unparalleled. Finished in immaculate Laguna Seca Blue with zero oxidation, the exterior matches the pristine cabin. Every bushing, fluid, and seal has been maintained to factory tolerances, offering a turnkey experience for the discerning purist.",
